<ab facs="#facs_250_r1l16">dem <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>gnedıgıſt<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ~ dem <expan>Römiſch<ex>en</ex></expan> etc kunıg ʒudıenſt </ab>
